title: Best Bits with Morgan and Special Guest Eddie: PART 1
itunes:title: Best Bits with Morgan and Special Guest Eddie: PART 1
description:
On this weeks episode of PART 1, you’ll hear Morgan and Eddie getting into their deep conversations about life. Morgan discusses in full detail her trip to Disney, and Eddie talks about some things he’s been up to with his family lately. They discuss mistakes not to make in your 20s as well as their perfect French Fry combination.  

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
